description:
Join us for our guest speaker event for the Iranian Feminist Resistance Movement! There will also be food + beverages, and fun activities where you can win prizes of $20+! Scan the QR code to make a donation to attend our event! You can also find the link in our bio! Can’t wait to see you all!💛

#iranianfeminists #amnestyinternational

A recap of our Run for Rights event for the Iranian Feminist Resistance Movement!💛 Thank you to everyone who joined and donated! Stay tuned for our upcoming events! 

#amnestyinternational #iranianfeminists

This month, Amnesty McGill is spotlighting the Iranian feminist resistance movement. Join us at our donation tables, charity run, and guest speaker event as we work to raise funds and awareness. Stay tuned for informative infographics throughout the month!
